current_subtask:
  summary: Make the release pipeline deterministic after the completed app passed all product and phone checks.
  verified:
    - one app chooser only; no duplicate intro
    - completion replaces the chooser and is immediately visible
    - exact kernel gate: 20 THINGS, gate 0.879, saturation
    - Reddit one-tap import refreshes the live feed to 1 THING
    - zero page reloads and zero late observer callbacks
    - overlay integrity and kernel parity green
  release_risk:
    - the PR Pages job is stalled in an external forum fetch unrelated to the manual app
    - the same unbounded third-party fetch would threaten the main deployment
  fix:
    - PR Pages checks assemble and verify the manual product without rebuilding the public root corpus
    - main pushes still build the full root corpus
    - public forum, social, and media retrieval on main get explicit time bounds and valid fallbacks
    - production artifact verification and phone smoke tests remain blocking
  done_when: PR 43 has four green checks quickly, and the main release cannot be held indefinitely by external content APIs.

